h: Three killed in Tinsukia Road accident
Assam: Two killed in Tinsukia Road accident
sub_h: Two persons, identified as Sukalyan Baruah (22) and Ripunjoy Phukan (28), died on the spot.

h: 7 students of Assam Engineering College killed, 5 injured in Road accident in Guwahati's Jalukbari
sub_h: As many as seven students were killed while a few others sustained injuries in a Road accident that happened at Jalukbari area in Assam's Guwahati late on Sunday night, said police.

h: Assam: Woman cop who nabbed fiance killed in Road accident
sub_h: A woman sub-inspector of Assam Police, who was in the news last year for arresting her fiance months before wedding for allegedly duping huge funds from two contractors in Majuli, was killed in a Road accident under mysterious circumstances in Nagaon district after her car allegedly collided with a truck on NH-37 early on Tuesday, the police said.

h: 3 killed, 7 injured in S Assam accidents
Seven students killed in Guwahati Road accident
3 of Nepalese family die in Sadiya Road accident
Rs 2 lakh each for kin of 3 Road accident victims at Dikom
sub_h: The state government has announced financial assistance of Rs 2 lakh each to the families of the Road accident victims at Dikom in Dibrugarh district.

h: Villagers block road, protest after youth dies in accident in Assam's Cachar
sub_h: Villagers of Dhumkar at Kalain locality in Cachar district staged a protest on Saturday against the death of a youth in a Road accident on Friday by blocking the Silchar-Kalain road for four hours.

h: 2 killed, 5 injured in Road accident in Assam’s Dhubri district
sub_h: Two girls were killed and five others injured in a Road accident in Assam’s Dhubri district, police said on Thursday.

h: Over 250 hurt in Road accidents in state during Holi
Seven killed, four injured in Road accidents in Assam
sub_h: At least seven people were killed and four injured in separate Road accidents in different parts of Assam on Thursday, police said.

h: 5 on way to attend wedding die in Nagaon Road accident
sub_h: Five youths going to attend a wedding ceremony were killed in a Road accident after their vehicle hit a truck at Hatiakhuwa in Nagaon on Monday night. The deceased have been identified as Bibek Das (26), Sanjai Das (26), Samir Paul (25), Bibek Sharma (26) and Sandeep Paul (26).

h: 3 IIIT-Guwahati students die in Kamrup Road accident
sub_h: Three students of the Indian Institute of Information Technology, Guwahati (IIIT-G), died in a Road accident while they were returning from a picnic spot in Chandubi, located on the outskirts of the city.

h: Three IIIT-Guwahati students killed in Road accident
sub_h: Three students of Indian Institute of Information Technology Guwahati (IIIT-G) died when the car, in which they were travelling, rolled over and fell into a nearby field.

h: Assam records 19% rise in Road accidents during Puja
sub_h: Assam reported a nearly 19% rise in Road accidents during Durga Puja from October 1 to Thursday, compared to last year.The festival was celebrated without any Covid-19 restriction after a gap of two years, which itself explains why the state witnessed a sharp rise in accidents.

h: 3 killed in Mizoram Road accident
sub_h: Three residents of Assam’s Cachar district were killed in a Road accident in Mizoram on Sunday night. Sources said the victims were returning home to celebrate Eid.The deceased persons have been identified as Jalil Uddin Laskar (50), Ramiz Uddin (26) and Ripon Uddin Laskar (21).

h: 1 dead, three injured in Assam Road accident
sub_h: A woman was killed and three persons, including an elderly woman, suffered injuries after a car in which they were travelling rammed into a bridge on the East-West corridor at Dolu in Borkhola of Cachar district on Friday night.

h: Assam: 3 Sipajhar friends, who died in Road accident, pass board exams
sub_h: On a day, the education department in Assam declared its class X board exam results, a pall of gloom descended in bustling Sipajhar town, as three boys, who died in a horrific Road accident on May 24, had easily cleared the exams.

h: Assam: Nine killed as autorickshaw collides with truck in Karimganj
sub_h: Nine passengers, all teenagers, died on the spot on Thursday morning when the autorickshaw in which they were travelling collided with a truck at Baithakhal on NH-8 in Karimganj district, Assam.

h: Five of a Bihu troupe killed in Road accident in Assam's Biswanath district
sub_h: Five of a Bihu troupe died on the spot while seven others were injured in a Road accident in northern Assam's Biswanath district in the wee hours of Sunday.

h: Day after 5 Bihu artistes die in Sivasagar Road accident, vehicle driver surrenders
sub_h: The driver of the vehicle, which met with an accident in Biswanath district on Sunday killing five Bihu artistes, surrendered at the Amguri police station in Sivasagar district on Monday. The driver, who has been identified as Abhijit Gogoi, was absconding since the incident.

h: Assam: Police file chargesheets against Rajkanya Baruah & man who 'killed cousin sister'
sub_h: Police here on Tuesday filed chargesheets against Rajkanya Baruah, accused in a Road accident that took place on October 2, and Abhishek Gupta in a murder case that took place on September 1.

h: 7 killed, 9 injured in Road accidents in Assam
sub_h: Four people were killed and eight others injured when an ambulance collided with a tempo at Baihata Chariali in Kamrup (Rural) district late on Friday night.

h: Assam: Three killed, 23 injured in Road accidents
sub_h: Three persons were killed and 23 others injured in three separate Road accidents in Assam, police said on Saturday.

h: 7 killed, 20 injured as bus rams into truck in Assam
sub_h: Seven people were killed and 20 others injured after a passenger bus collided head-on with a truck on National Highway-17 in Assam's Kokrajhar district on Sunday, police said.

h: Accidents claim three, injure 23 in Assam
sub_h: Three persons were killed and 23 others injured in three separate Road accidents in Assam.

h: Tinsukia journo, who wrote against corruption, dies in Road accident
